 @{fg shine}Fonts:@{fg text}


 I have tried to design the best font within the constraints set by the
 FunFont criteria, and as of version 2.2 there is now a choice of @{fg fill}@{bg shine}þ12@{fg text}@{bg background}
 different fonts with varying height, width and weights.
 

